Package ca.ualberta.taskr.models.elasticsearch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callback<T>
    Callback interface for determining whether an asyncronous network operation was succesfull or not
    ElasticSearch
    ElasticSearch Interface. This interface defines the specific search queries to be performed
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachingRetrofit
    CachingRetrofit class. This class is responsible for fetching cached data and locally mocking Retrofit calls instead of trying to grab results via elasticsearch
    ElasticsearchID
    ElasticSearch ID container class. This class essentially an immutable String with a different name
    GenerateRetrofit
    GenerateRetrofit Class This class acts as a wrapper to the REST api functionality and ElasticSearch calls, as well as providing data serialization using GSON and JSON for queried objects
    Query
    Query class. Allows for the querying of lists of objects, create RequestBodies for different elasticsearch queries.
    ServerInfo
    ServerInfo Class. Contains various information relating to connection status
